data.description: 160 Darcy Ave is ready for you to make it yours today! Huge Price reduction to accomadate any Buyer Desire you may have along with 2year old kitchen appliances there to keep!!When you walk in, this open concept space feels huge with its vaulted ceilings, double windows throughout, french doors, and tons of natural light. A well appointed kitchen sits to the right which includes gorgeous windows, stainless appliances, tile floors, and loads of storage space.  The downstair Master bedroom off of living room has plenty of space for a large bedroom suite while including a tile floored ensuite and a walk in closet. Upstairs you'll find 2 guest rooms with ample closet space and a large hall bathroom.  The garage has been converted to a gym space/playroom but can be returned easily by buyer.
